// as ess method meh:
// for "pre-order-traversal" apnko simply sbse-phle sbse-left-most-node select krna hai and bas likh dena hai. or otherwise thode acche or or thode sahi se bole toh sbse phle apnko bottom-of-tree( as apnko yeh dhyn  meh rkhna hai ki yaha programming meh apn tree ko "inverted"-position meh draw krtehh hai for the sake-of-simplicity ) meh ek line draw krleni hai then phir sbhi left-most-nodes ko uss linke se connect kr lena hai and then phir at-the-end uss bottom-line connected sbhi lines ko from left-to-right notedown krlena hai ki konsi line konse node se connected hai and vohi apna pre-order-traversal-result hoga.

// and for "in-order-traversal" apnko simply middle-nodes ko bottom-line pe connect krna hai and then phir at-last apnko uss bottom-line ko from lef-to-right scan kr lena hai ki esseh connected lines pe konsa node hai.

// and for "post-order-traversal" k liyeh apnko simply right-most-nodes ko bottom-line se connect krna hai and then at-last bottom-line ko from left-to-right scan krke apna traversal-result likh lena hai.

